WEBVTT

00:00:00.140 --> 00:00:03.060
=The Crow Princess of Fortune=

00:00:03.060 --> 00:00:04.980
=Episode 12=

00:00:04.980 --> 00:00:06.160
You're just a picked up wild girl.

00:00:06.160 --> 00:00:07.920
What makes you think
you're worthy of studying with us?

00:00:07.920 --> 00:00:09.579
Yeah. Who do you think you are?

00:00:09.580 --> 00:00:12.100
Who I am isn't important.

00:00:22.060 --> 00:00:24.060
What's important is...

00:00:28.500 --> 00:00:29.570
Lin Yu,

00:00:29.680 --> 00:00:33.140
last month you stole your father's
jade pendant and pawned it,

00:00:33.300 --> 00:00:34.640
then lost fifty taels

00:00:34.640 --> 00:00:38.420
(Lin Yu, son of the Minister of Revenue)
at the gambling house.

00:00:38.460 --> 00:00:42.260
Your jade pendant
is still sitting in the pawnshop.

00:00:42.300 --> 00:00:44.219
It'll cost eighty taels to redeem it.

00:00:44.220 --> 00:00:47.219
Want me to tell your father?

00:00:47.220 --> 00:00:47.699
You...

00:00:47.700 --> 00:00:49.180
How do you know that?

00:00:52.980 --> 00:00:54.099
Su Mingyuan,

00:00:54.100 --> 00:00:56.359
last month you harassed a young girl

00:00:56.360 --> 00:00:57.280
(Su Mingyuan)
on the street

00:00:57.280 --> 00:00:59.179
(Son of the Minister of Military Affairs)
and got chased through three streets.

00:00:59.180 --> 00:01:01.500
In the end,
you hid in a latrine to escape.

00:01:02.820 --> 00:01:05.259
Lu Yan, you cheated on yesterday's exam.

00:01:05.260 --> 00:01:07.619
You hid your cheat sheet in your sleeve,

00:01:07.620 --> 00:01:09.619
but it accidentally fell out

00:01:09.620 --> 00:01:11.059
and Zhao Qi picked it up.

00:01:11.060 --> 00:01:13.640
You spent five taels to keep him quiet.

00:01:13.640 --> 00:01:15.360
(Lu Yan, son of the Minister
of the Court of Imperial Sacrifices)

00:01:16.260 --> 00:01:18.619
Anyone else want to hear their story?

00:01:18.620 --> 00:01:22.260
I've got plenty more stories.

00:01:22.380 --> 00:01:23.899
And the price is reasonable too.

00:01:23.900 --> 00:01:25.700
Only five taels each.

00:01:26.860 --> 00:01:29.260
Your Highness, this girl is terrifying.

00:01:29.580 --> 00:01:31.020
During riding class later,

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:33.020
I'll deal with her myself.

00:01:33.580 --> 00:01:34.479
That's right.

00:01:34.480 --> 00:01:37.779
The eldest imperial grandson was personally
taught horseback riding by the Crown Prince.

00:01:37.780 --> 00:01:38.819
No one can beat him,

00:01:38.820 --> 00:01:41.180
let alone some little girl.

00:01:41.620 --> 00:01:43.019
During riding class later,

00:01:43.020 --> 00:01:46.060
Your Highness, show her what you've got.
Teach her a lesson.

00:01:50.940 --> 00:01:52.879
(Fun Racecourse Begins)
At the sound of the gong, Suisui's little pink horse

00:01:52.880 --> 00:01:54.000
(Charge Forward)
shot out like an arrow,

00:01:54.000 --> 00:01:54.960
leaving everyone far behind.

00:01:54.960 --> 00:01:55.960
Go! Charge forward!

00:01:55.960 --> 00:01:58.520
Congratulations to Princess Suisui
for winning the race with ease!

00:02:01.500 --> 00:02:02.219
She...

00:02:02.220 --> 00:02:03.980
She crossed the finish line
with His Highness.

00:02:04.020 --> 00:02:05.099
Not together.

00:02:05.100 --> 00:02:06.979
She was half
a horse length ahead of him.

00:02:06.980 --> 00:02:08.099
How is that possible?

00:02:08.100 --> 00:02:10.539
His Highness was personally
taught riding by the Crown Prince.

00:02:10.540 --> 00:02:11.980
And she's just some picked up...

00:02:12.520 --> 00:02:13.339
Keep your voice down.

00:02:13.340 --> 00:02:14.159
What if she hears you

00:02:14.160 --> 00:02:15.579
and exposes your secrets too?

00:02:15.580 --> 00:02:16.899
Still too slow.

00:02:16.900 --> 00:02:18.440
You only get half a carrot.

00:02:18.440 --> 00:02:20.960
What a ruthless merchant.
You promised me one whole carrot.

00:02:20.960 --> 00:02:23.340
Keep arguing
and you won't get even half.

00:02:27.780 --> 00:02:28.619
So?

00:02:28.620 --> 00:02:31.659
How about paying me some tuition?
I'll give you the family discount.

00:02:31.660 --> 00:02:32.379
(Father said...)

00:02:32.380 --> 00:02:33.899
(If I can't even beat her
at the academy,)

00:02:33.900 --> 00:02:35.540
(then I don't deserve to be his son.)

00:02:40.260 --> 00:02:41.700
I want to ride this horse.

00:02:41.860 --> 00:02:43.379
Your Highness, this horse is dangerous.

00:02:43.380 --> 00:02:44.379
Its temper is too wild.

00:02:44.380 --> 00:02:46.020
It's already injured many people.

00:02:46.220 --> 00:02:47.939
Ordinary horses are beneath me.

00:02:47.940 --> 00:02:50.700
If I'm going to ride one,
I'll ride the best.

00:02:51.340 --> 00:02:52.259
Xiao Suisui,

00:02:52.260 --> 00:02:55.500
do you dare race me again?

00:02:58.140 --> 00:03:01.020
This is bad. Stay away from that horse.

00:03:04.060 --> 00:03:05.180
Oh no!

00:03:05.260 --> 00:03:06.299
The horse has gone mad!

00:03:06.300 --> 00:03:07.820
No one can control it!

00:03:10.820 --> 00:03:11.980
Stand still.

00:03:15.660 --> 00:03:17.300
I said stand still!

00:03:20.500 --> 00:03:21.979
You've got some nerve.

00:03:21.980 --> 00:03:23.459
Who are you trying to scare?

00:03:23.460 --> 00:03:24.939
If you dare scare people again,

00:03:24.940 --> 00:03:27.179
I'll send you to turn the mill.

00:03:27.180 --> 00:03:29.819
You'll work all day until you drop.

00:03:29.820 --> 00:03:30.979
Sorry.

00:03:30.980 --> 00:03:32.659
Do you know what you did wrong now?

00:03:32.660 --> 00:03:33.899
Behave yourself from now on.

00:03:33.900 --> 00:03:35.740
No more scaring people.

00:03:38.940 --> 00:03:40.380
Xiao Rui.

00:03:41.300 --> 00:03:42.899
Who said I was helping you up?

00:03:42.900 --> 00:03:44.939
Rescue fee, fifty taels.

00:03:44.940 --> 00:03:47.219
Appearance fee, another thirty.

00:03:47.220 --> 00:03:48.739
That's eighty taels total. Pay up.

00:03:48.740 --> 00:03:51.140
And if you want me to help you up,

00:03:51.180 --> 00:03:52.500
that's another ten taels.

00:03:52.620 --> 00:03:55.700
She's crazy. There's no way
His Highness would pay her.

00:04:03.380 --> 00:04:04.460
Is this enough?

00:04:05.620 --> 00:04:06.980
More than enough.

00:04:09.740 --> 00:04:10.660
What?

00:04:18.240 --> 00:04:21.559
♪Little lucky star,
twinkling with a wink at me♪

00:04:21.560 --> 00:04:25.399
♪Every Chinese New Year day brings
the luckiest fortune slip♪

00:04:25.400 --> 00:04:28.919
♪The God of Wealth favors me,
the Matchmaker ties red strings for me♪

00:04:28.920 --> 00:04:31.880
♪With firecrackers going off,
good things keep coming one after another♪

00:04:32.760 --> 00:04:36.399
♪Make a wish on the very first day
of the Chinese New Year♪

00:04:36.400 --> 00:04:40.160
♪By the second day,
my belly's already round♪

00:04:40.240 --> 00:04:43.559
♪Always talking about dieting,
but the chub never disappears♪

00:04:43.560 --> 00:04:47.600
♪Good food brings joy
and happiness every single day♪

00:04:53.200 --> 00:04:56.879
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
every year is filled with joy♪

00:04:56.880 --> 00:05:00.519
♪I'm bringing blessings to everyone♪

00:05:00.520 --> 00:05:04.239
♪Hands clasped together in greeting♪

00:05:04.240 --> 00:05:07.879
♪May every family be sweet and happy♪

00:05:07.880 --> 00:05:11.559
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
may everything go your way♪

00:05:11.560 --> 00:05:13.479
♪Endlessly flowing♪

00:05:13.480 --> 00:05:19.680
♪Good fortune♪